"title" = "About MONA";

"preamble" = "Discover the city of Montreal and its art with a free and fun app, MONA.\n\nThe city becomes your playground. Search for art and take a photo to add it to your personal collection. Keep tabs on your experience by adding your own ratings and comments. As you roam through Montreal's districts and collect artworks, you will win rewards recognizing your dedication as art collector.\n\nMONA is a free and open source project aiming for all people to discover and enjoy public art. Find out more about our philosophy on our website: http://www.artetsite.org/mona .\n\nMONA is an academic research project based in Montreal, Canada. As detailed in Privacy Policy, the data we collect only serves the purpose of academic research. The project is entirely non-commercial and no third parties are involved.";

