"contributors title" = "Contributors";
"contributors body" = "MONA was created with the support of the research group \"art+site\", the Faculty of Arts and Science of the Université de Montréal and its Departement of Art History and Cinematographic Studies, in collaboration with the Department of Computer Science and Operations Research and the School of Design of the University. We have also received support from the Montreal Public Art Bureau.\n\nIf you would like to contribute to MONA in any form and share feedback with us, please do not hesitate to contact us at mona-app@tutanota.com. We'd love to hear from you!";
